    "cloudimage_help" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\nThe image could be one of local raw image, qcow2 cloud image, lxc simplestreams image, oci image, ipsw or iso\nImage format is determined by url scheme or extension\nThe url image form are:\n  - local images (raw format): /Users/myhome/disk.img or file:///Users/myhome/disk.img\n  - local qcow2 images: /Users/myhome/disk.qcow2 or qcow2:///Users/myhome/disk.img\n  - unsecure remote cloud images (qcow2 format): http://cloud-images.ubuntu.com/releases/noble/release/ubuntu-24.04-server-cloudimg-arm64.img\n  - secure remote cloud images (qcow2 format): https://cloud-images.ubuntu.com/releases/noble/release/ubuntu-24.04-server-cloudimg-arm64.img\n  - lxc images: images:ubuntu/noble/cloud, see remote command for detail\n  - secure oci images (tart format): ocis://ghcr.io/cirruslabs/ubuntu:latest (https)\n  - unsecure oci images (tart format): oci://unsecure.com/ubuntu:latest (http)\n  - local macos restore: /Users/myhome/restore.ipsw or ipsw:///Users/myhome/restore\n  - remote macos restore: ipsw://ipsw.me/install/Mac17,4/25D2128\n  - local iso: /Users/myhome/disk.iso or iso:///Users/myhome/disk\n  - unsecure remote iso: http://cdimage.ubuntu.com/releases/26.04/snapshot-4/ubuntu-26.04-snapshot4-desktop-arm64.iso or iso://cdimage.nowhere.com/releases/latest\n  - secure remote iso: https://cdimage.ubuntu.com/releases/26.04/snapshot-4/ubuntu-26.04-snapshot4-desktop-arm64.iso or isos://cdimage.nowhere.com/releases/latest\n"
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\nL'image peut être une image au format RAW, une image cloud au format qcow2, une image LXC Simplestreams, une image OCI, un fichier IPSW ou ISO.\nLe format de l'image est déterminé par le schéma d'URL ou son extension.\nVoici les formats d'URL des images :\n    - Images locales (format RAW) : /Users/myhome/disk.img ou file:///Users/myhome/disk.img\n    - Images qcow2 locales : /Users/myhome/disk.qcow2 ou qcow2:///Users/myhome/disk.img\n    - Images cloud distantes non sécurisées (format qcow2) : http://cloud-images.ubuntu.com/releases/noble/release/ubuntu-24.04-server-cloudimg-arm64.img\n    - Images cloud distantes sécurisées (format qcow2) : https://cloud-images.ubuntu.com/releases/noble/release/ubuntu-24.04-server-cloudimg-arm64.img\n    - Images LXC/Incus : images:ubuntu/noble/cloud, voir la commande à distance pour plus de détails\n    - Images OCI sécurisées (format tart) : ocis://ghcr.io/cirruslabs/ubuntu:latest (https)\n    - Images OCI non sécurisées (format tart) : oci://unsecure.com/ubuntu:latest (http)\n    - Restauration macOS locale : /Users/myhome/restore.ipsw ou ipsw:///Users/myhome/restore\n    - Restauration macOS distante : ipsw://ipsw.me/install/Mac17,4/25D2128\n    - ISO locale : /Users/myhome/disk.iso ou iso:///Users/myhome/disk\n    - ISO distant non sécurisée : http://cdimage.ubuntu.com/releases/26.04/snapshot-4/ubuntu-26.04-snapshot4-desktop-arm64.iso ou iso://cdimage.nowhere.com/releases/latest\n    - ISO distant sécurisé : https://cdimage.ubuntu.com/releases/26.04/snapshot-4/ubuntu-26.04-snapshot4-desktop-arm64.iso ou isos://cdimage.nowhere.com/releases/latest\n"
          }
        }
      }
    },
